| Dominio                      | Funzioni                                                                                                                                                                           |
| ---------------------------- | ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| Pairing                      | `pair-init`, `pair-claim`, `pair-direct`, `pair-revoke`                                                                                                                            |
| Room player                  | `room-player-bootstrap`, `room-state-set`, `room-state-broadcast`                                                                                                                  |
| Upload (TUS + speaker)       | `upload-init`, `upload-finalize`, `room-device-upload-init`, `room-device-upload-finalize`, `slide-validator`                                                                       |
| Licensing                    | `licensing-sync`, `lemon-squeezy-webhook`                                                                                                                                          |
| GDPR / Email / Monitoring    | `gdpr-export`, `gdpr-delete`, `email-sender`, `monitoring-snapshot`, `monitoring-cron`, `cleanup-cron`, `super-admin-snapshot`                                                     |
| Auth / Rate-limit (shared)   | `_shared/cors.ts`, `_shared/rate-limit.ts`, `_shared/auth.ts` (helper, non endpoint), oltre a `auth-passwordless`, `auth-invite-accept`, `tenant-suspend`, `tenant-onboard`         |

`verify_jwt`: tutte ON tranne `pair-claim`, `room-player-bootstrap`, `lemon-squeezy-webhook`, `slide-validator` (anon by design).

## Edge Functions — flussi reali

### Pairing PC sala (cloud)

```
Admin SPA → pair-init (JWT)        → INSERT pairing_codes (code 6 cifre, expires 10 min)
                                   ← {code: '123456', expires_at}
[Mostra codice all'utente]
PC sala  → pair-claim (no auth)    → SELECT pairing_codes by code → INSERT paired_devices
                                       (con pair_token_hash = sha256(random_bytes(32)))
                                     UPDATE pairing_codes SET consumed_at = NOW()
                                   ← {device_token: '<random-32-byte-hex>', room_state: {...}}
PC sala  → room-player-bootstrap   → ogni 12-60s (Sprint A playback_mode tuning)
        (device_token)             ← {presentation_versions, network_mode, agent LAN, manifest}
```

### Pairing LAN-direct (Sprint N — admin desktop ↔ sala desktop)

```
Admin Tauri  → cmd_discover_lan_pcs(role='sala') → mDNS browse 1500ms
                                                  → [{name, addresses, port, txt}]
Admin SPA    → genera codice 6 cifre client-side
Admin Tauri  → pair_direct_lan({targetBaseUrl})  → POST http://<sala>:<port>/functions/v1/pair-direct
                                                    body: {code, device_name, event_id, room_id}
Sala server  → valida codice (window 5s) → INSERT paired_devices LOCALE
                                            persisti device.json
                                          ← {device_token, paired_devices: {...}}
Admin Tauri  → registerPairedDeviceOnAdminLocal → POST /rest/v1/paired_devices LOCALE admin
                                                  (mirror per fan-out futuro)
```

### GDPR export (Sprint 7)

```
Admin SPA → gdpr-export (JWT admin) → RPC public.gdpr_export_tenant_data(tenant_id)
                                       (SECURITY DEFINER, bypassa RLS solo per export)
                                     ZIP service-role: events.json + rooms.json + sessions.json
                                       + presentations.json + audit.json
                                     UPLOAD su Storage path tenants/<id>/exports/<timestamp>.zip
                                   → signed URL 7g
```

